{"id":"4b15f67a1cc4799ae81317f8b12d2ad89ae96b0458017f7494b7da65111f12e4","item_id":"6d22673120:0","text":"此 pattern 会程序化创建矩形或六边形网格，并且可以连接额外的 pattern 来控制颜色和边框厚度。"}
{"id":"7e744141b40ea5501412e42c8b40fd0b05f1608aa2e4073944ccccbd82f24ee8","item_id":"6d22673120:1","text":"Style"}
{"id":"3dd88f81fe5705dbeb3ab25296f6b29309e702de66b262fd3fd2eed454789b64","item_id":"6d22673120:2","text":"定义要渲染的 pattern 形状。"}
{"id":"f517ee3c1d3043381ef72754f0bfb9b5c0fa861106f3d26ab30d10cf85fb8637","item_id":"6d22673120:3","text":"Rectangular -"}
{"id":"da29d07e125664c3fa24b70580692826a74d28ec69d64a3e630b925b2d52aff9","item_id":"6d22673120:4","text":"此 pattern 会重复四边形形状"}
{"id":"026a83d639efb087d4b0d391f6d31a909e73c7b6573222ff7adec696bdf14792","item_id":"6d22673120:5","text":"Hexagonal -"}
{"id":"8ca84683fcd896b94f4d750612d55957c5aec692d83a7773b62ede0267fd4ddc","item_id":"6d22673120:6","text":"此 pattern 会重复具有 uniform（均匀）外观的六边形形状"}
{"id":"131092767de54859e80652223f3a1c6cc5a24b2274288bb6129bba8b72d8df24","item_id":"6d22673120:7","text":"Tile Width"}
{"id":"23011f4194938a3caf577ad3d2c9ad760b633e6ec18ac518750a247a3029923f","item_id":"6d22673120:8","text":"设置内部形状的 width（宽度）尺寸；小于 1.0 的值会产生额外重复。使用 Hexagonal 时，会采用 Width 或 Height 中的最小值。"}
{"id":"9a3d3c194e3bc3b651e62706bfc54dae5fc0a68310883d36d8b2073bfb5aa270","item_id":"6d22673120:9","text":"Tile Height"}
{"id":"1cb08076ae4b4daec180ab5135e331c2ef9ee1ed5e0586cf233c5b47a0d4cf4c","item_id":"6d22673120:10","text":"设置内部形状的高度尺寸；小于 1.0 的值会产生额外重复。使用 Hexagonal 时，会采用 Width 或 Height 中的最小值。"}
{"id":"0360da1adef102fcc3b7c514dc9017b5a96cd7219e20f863164719dfbb9c50c2","item_id":"6d22673120:11","text":"Tile Shift"}
{"id":"20b5088cdf681f63b7981aba8b22ce45631cde967aede58bda08c91932f68e05","item_id":"6d22673120:12","text":"偏移隔行。默认值 0 会创建规则网格，而 0.5 会创建砖块状布局。"}
{"id":"31287ec4e275d1bebcfce24dcfab040686f15a1795e88741e0e4f7f16d70d5fe","item_id":"6d22673120:13","text":"Border Thickness"}
{"id":"b60220e64881be7a01237a3fa3881a6a450a6541c2e69a85f5e41b144fa3008d","item_id":"6d22673120:14","text":"设置每个 tile 的边框尺寸，并且在修改 tile 的 width（宽度）和高度时保持不变。"}
{"id":"d17f785cab3f66ed5f0a4e751beab9834eef29dd068e7ed159110f41683115ba","item_id":"6d22673120:15","text":"Color Tile"}
{"id":"a07770593e1bb3e9cdd48e602055dfb15210e9546562eaf798df761bda0d85b8","item_id":"6d22673120:16","text":"按 width（宽度）和高度定义，设置每个 tile 内部的颜色。"}
{"id":"1a9834dbb324b6df2a822b5fb335f3200a367cfd6b85e214e9670402622043c4","item_id":"6d22673120:17","text":"Color Border"}
{"id":"22906843965d79f8f3b8da8b9fb2fa8266bf0d93b79881579ea899507e76403b","item_id":"6d22673120:18","text":"按边框厚度定义，设置每个 tile 边框的颜色。"}
{"id":"7b2b1d558b951cab5d877547a3ec14a7d8305b359243d69178b6ad63d298832e","item_id":"6d22673120:20","text":"可在此应用一个 manifold utility，用来调整 pattern 在表面上的位置以及其他属性。"}
{"id": "e29793dea8429f58cc913ce697117a3614eaa231b5a3942af954b66c44d43850", "item_id": "6d22673120:19", "text": "Manifold"}
